'''Shotacon''', like lolicon, is a [[CP|child-pornographic]] sub-genre of [[hentai]] featuring underage boys (aka ''shota''). It typically focuses on prepubescent boys having wild [[gay]] [[sex]], though in real life this would never happen because they're more busy playing [[X-box]] than playing with their shriveled penises. Essentially, shotacon is [[yaoi]], only younger and with fewer pubes.

Shotacon should not be confused with 'Shotokan', a form of [[karate]], except when (carefully!) [[troll]]ing boards frequented by practitioners of that style. If you do this on an Okinawan Goju-ryu board and they might give you a fucking black belt, at which point you should [[An hero]].

